latestPosts.caption:
From clean organic ingredients to mindful formulations, every Ruby’s Organics product is crafted with care. 💜 Experience uncomplicated, plant-based products thoughtfully designed for Indian skin. Give clean beauty a chance—give Ruby’s Organics a chance. 🌿 Makeup made better. 🥰

#founder #brandstory #naturalbeauty #organicbeauty #rubysorganics

#ELLESustainabilityAwards2024: Rubeina Karachiwalla (@rubeina.k), Founder of @rubys.organics, has changed the perception of beauty products, highlighting the importance of clean, organic materials and environmentally responsible packaging. Being a trailblazer in the sustainable cosmetics industry, Rubeina has proven her unwavering commitment to making products that respect and protect the environment while enhancing natural beauty. Beyond her entrepreneurial success, Rubeina Karachiwalla is a tireless advocate for environmental conservation and social responsibility. It was thus fitting to present her with the ELLE Beauty Changemaker Award. 
.
Presented by Signature Packaged Drinking Water (@signaturegreenvibes)

latestPosts.caption:
Here’s a quick tutorial on how to best use our Tinted Eyebrow Gels in 3 easy steps 😎:

1. Wipe off excess product.
2. Fill in brows from the middle outward.
3. Stroke upward for naturally fuller, thicker brows. 

The best part? If you have frizzy/baby hair or grey hair, you can use this to touch up or fill in any scanty patches 😲

#rubysorganics #eyebrowtutorial #browgame #browgoals #eyebrowtransformation #fullerbrows #veganbeauty #easymakeup #explorepage

latestPosts.caption:
We can’t keep calm, we have big news! 🎉

Our heart is bursting with joy as our Lip Oil Glosses won the Elle Beauty Award 2022 as the best product in the lip category 🥰

To be the only organic beauty brand to be nominated in the lip category with the best from the industry globally, and to win is truly an honour 🥹❤

Here’s raising a toast to our Ruby’s fam, we love you the most! 🥂 

We couldn’t have done this without your unwavering support and constant love. We hope to continue to inspire you every day as you deserve nothing but the very best 💯 

#rubysorganics #awardwinning #awardwinner #ellebeautyawards2022 #lipoilgloss #lipgloss #rubysfam #overwhelmed #milestone #cleanbeauty #organicbeauty #crueltyfreebeauty
